This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use the Tabibak - طبيبك mobile application.

Information Collection and Use

The Tabibak - طبيبك app facilitates communication between doctors and patients, including chat functionality. When you use the app, we may collect and store certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to:

Your name
Contact information (such as email address, phone number)
Medical information shared during consultations
Chat history between doctors and patients
Documents, videos, and images shared with doctors
We use this information to provide you with access to our services and to improve and personalize your experience with the app. We do not share or disclose your personal information with third parties, except as described in this Privacy Policy.

Data Security

We are committed to protecting the security of your personal information and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard it. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Access to Documents, Videos, and Images

We respect your privacy and understand the sensitive nature of medical information. Any documents, videos, or images shared with doctors through the app are strictly confidential and are only accessible by you and the designated healthcare professionals involved in your care. No one else, including our staff, will have access to these files without your explicit consent, except as required by law.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at hamza.hajhamad@gmail.com.

By using the Tabibak - طبيبك app, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
